60
00:04:37,946 --> 00:04:41,426
<font color=#FFFF00>Ich tue etwas Honig drauf.</font>

61
00:04:43,866 --> 00:04:47,346
<font color=#FFFF00>Es gibt den Mythos,</font>

62
00:04:48,306 --> 00:04:51,666
<font color=#FFFF00>dass man Linsen nicht</font>
<font color=#FFFF00>in Salzwasser garen soll.</font>

63
00:04:51,826 --> 00:04:55,186
